* Data model
** literals
*** integer
212         /* Legal */
215u        /* Legal */
0xFeeL      /* Legal */
078         /* Illegal: 8 is not an octal digit */
032UU       /* Illegal: cannot repeat a suffix */
85         /* decimal, int */
0213       /* octal, int */
0x4b       /* hexadecimal */
30         /* int */
30u, 30U   /* unsigned int */
30l, 30L   /* long */
30ul       /* unsigned long */

*** float
3.14159       /* Legal */
314159E-5L    /* Legal */
510E          /* Illegal: incomplete exponent */
210f          /* Illegal: no decimal or exponent */
.e55          /* Illegal: missing integer or fraction */
